metadata.title: Crypto Bahamas Wrap up Party!
metadata.name: Crypto Bahamas Wrap up Party!
metadata.description: NFT invitation to a private Crypto Bahamas wrap-up party at The Cove at Atlantis on April 29th at 7pm Eastern Standard Time. The NFT includes food and drinks. There will also be a fire show for attendees!
